webpackJsonp([0x8b88ba961ff9],{8679:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"The American Dory",date:"07 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-07-the-american-dory/",tags:"Y2003"},html:"<p>Christopher's Christmas package from Minnesota arrived yesterday. And, I admit it, I just had to take a peek... at the Finding Nemo DVD. Since the film was just released in Germany, it will be months before the DVD is available here. But it's OK. I'm an American citizen. I'm <em>allowed</em> to view Region 1 DVDs.</p>\n<p>My main suspicion was confirmed, namely that <a href=\"http://www.brainpool.de/en/stars/engelke/\">Anke Engelke</a>, the German voice of Dory, is a thousand times better than whoever did the original American Dory. But I was also disappointed. Dory's best line ('Kennen wir uns?', when she doesn't recognize Marlin the first time) is a dud in English ('Can I help you?').</p>"},next:{fields:{title:"Goodbye Lenin sweeps Europe Film Prize",date:"07 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-07-goodbye-lenin-sweeps-europe-film-prize/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"The Ghost of Schill",date:"07 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-07-the-ghost-of-schill/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Goodbye Lenin sweeps Europe Film Prize",date:"07 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-07-goodbye-lenin-sweeps-europe-film-prize/",tags:"Y2003"},html:'<p><a title="Oscar for Best Foreign Film?" href="http://www.reuters.co.uk/newsPackageArticle.jhtml?type=entertainmentNews&amp;storyID=416845&amp;section=news">Goodbye Lenin sweeps Europe Film Prize</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Christmas Stocking",date:"06 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-06-christmas-stocking/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"The American Dory",date:"07 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-07-the-american-dory/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Christmas Stocking",date:"06 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-06-christmas-stocking/",tags:"Y2003"},html:'<p><img alt="crh_stocking.jpg" src="http://www.papascott.de/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2003/12/crh_stocking.jpg" width="320" height="218" border="0" /></p>\n<p>Grandma sent Christopher a Christmas stocking. Since he\'s not familiar with American Christmas customs, he thought he had to wear it.</p>\n<p>We\'ll set it out for the <a href="http://www.training-for-germany.de/tips99/tip11.htm">Nikolaus</a> tonight. He\'s coming to our house a day late this year, and he\'s been informed to expect a stocking instead of a shoe. (The exact date doesn\'t matter, since Christopher is already a few days ahead with his Advent calendar.)</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"I nearly forgot my fourth weblog anniversary",date:"05 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-05-i-nearly-forgot-my-fourth-weblog-anniversary/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Goodbye Lenin sweeps Europe Film Prize",date:"07 Dec 2003",slug:"/2003-12-07-goodbye-lenin-sweeps-europe-film-prize/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:575,pageCount:1101}}}});
